snippet.title: Pokémon: Fat Kid Live-Action Trailer
snippet.description:
Live-Action Trailer for Pokémon: Fat Kid. An extended live-action trailer will come after the release of the beta.
For more information, visit: https://www.pokecommunity.com/showthread.php?t=333880

Subtitle track is included in the video.

Special thanks to actors Patrick and Trevor.

Music used in this video:
Alfa Flite - Love Games
Ace Trainer encounter music from the RSE games
Mewmore Dasgust - Rustboro City (Remix) 

If you need to contact me, you can at honchofilms@live.com
